### 3.3 — [MOBILE ONLY] Headline text can overflow on very narrow screens

| Detail | |
|---|---|
| **File** | [public.css:98-105](file:///c:/Users/Josep/Desktop/Resume_Project/Prototype_v2/css/public.css#L98-L105) |
